dct_title_s: Rutgers Alumni Monthly; New Brunswick, New Jersey
dct_description_sm: Cover to the October 1941 edition of the Rutgers Alumni Monthly. This issue features a picture map of the College Avenue Campus in New Brunswick, New Jersey. Buildings on the maps are dated and various historical events and places are noted in inset pictures.
